Rating: 2
This dish was ok. I think the marinade would have been better with some garlic and perhaps less orange zest (1 TBS vs 2). I also think the oven temp is too high as stated. I roasted mine at 375 for an hour and only got a few overly browned spots. I think there are probably better ways to prepare Cornish Game Hens.

